from typing import List

def generate_display_table(orders: List[List[str]]) -> List[List[str]]:
    record = defaultdict(lambda : defaultdict(int))
    for (_, table, item) in orders:
        record[table][item] -= 1
    items = sorted(set((item for v in record.values() for item in v.keys())))
    res = []
    for (table, v) in sorted(record.items(), key=lambda x: int(x[0])):
        res.append([table] + ['0' if item not in v else str(v[item]) for item in items])
    res = [['Table'] + items] + res
    return res
